thread.title_full: Lucky Tackle Box reviewed by Dan H

author: Dan H
title: Dan H
text:
I really love my Lucky Tackle Box, it is by far the best of the tackle subscriptions. The live streaming drawings and quizzes are fun to watch, so have your golden ticket ready.
Customer support staff like Britni are quick to respond to questions and resolve any problems a subscriber might have.
Thank you for being such a great origination for avid anglers of all types.
Dan H
